$ Excel: Formula bar
@ Formula bar

If shownn, the *Formula bar* is located below the → Microsoft/Office/GUI/Ribbon[Ribbon] and used to enter or edit values or → Microsoft/Office/Excel/formulas[formulas].

The visibility of the formula bar can be changed with the checkbox *Formulas* found in
→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/File/Options/Advanced#xls-opt-disp[File -> Options -> Advanced -> Display].

sa:

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Application/formulaBarHeight[`application.formulaBarHeight`]
